{"tid":2421301,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【財政預算案2021】中原陳永傑: 股票買賣加印花稅 料套股換樓增加","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T05:12:54.000Z","uid":166360,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"29a01dcd1d1145a7b2dd339abd2a9a1de866b542","tid":2421301,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"【財政預算案2021】中原陳永傑: 股票買賣加印花稅 料套股換樓增加<br />\n17:40 2021/02/24<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......於新一份財政預算案中，股票印花稅被調升，汽車首次登記稅及牌費亦增加，相比起以上兩項商品，物業市場並未於新一份財案中被加辣，相信套股換樓活動增加，部份資金將流向樓市。<br />\n<br />\n新財案繼續努力增加土地及住宅供應，未來5年私人住宅每年平均落成量約1.8萬個，較去年公布的1.96萬個，再進一步減少，相信政府覓地困難於短期內亦難解決，即使成功覓地，比例亦較著重公營房屋供應，相信未來私人住宅供應依然匱乏......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2885577/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%882021%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E9%99%B3%E6%B0%B8%E5%82%91:%20%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3%E5%8A%A0%E5%8D%B0%E8%8A%B1%E7%A8%85%20%E6%96%99%E5%A5%97%E8%82%A1%E6%8F%9B%E6%A8%93%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2885577%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%25882021%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258E%259F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%2582%2591%3A%2520%25E8%2582%25A1%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%25A8%2585%2520%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%25A5%2597%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%258F%259B%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8F8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=afacb1dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2885577/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%882021%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E9%99%B3%E6%B0%B8%E5%82%91:%20%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3%E5%8A%A0%E5%8D%B0%E8%8A%B1%E7%A8%85%20%E6%96%99%E5%A5%97%E8%82%A1%E6%8F%9B%E6%A8%93%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span c